{"id":458,"parent_id":454,"book_id":1,"content_id":1,"language_id":1,"display_order":458,"title":"Job 4","subtitle":"","short_title":"Job","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4","content":[["div",[".titleNumber","Chapter 4"],[".studySummary",["i","Eliphaz reproves Job, asking such questions as, Are the righteous cut off? Shall a man be more pure than his maker?"]]],[".bodyBlock",["div",{"id":"1","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.1","order":"02.19.004.33126"},["b","1"],"Then",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_1a"},"Eliphaz"],"the Temanite answered and said,"],["div",{"id":"2","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.2","order":"02.19.004.33127"},["b","2"],["i","If"],"we assay to commune with thee, wilt thou be grieved? but who can withhold himself from speaking?"],["div",{"id":"3","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.3","order":"02.19.004.33128"},["b","3"],"Behold, thou hast instructed many, and thou hast strengthened the weak hands."],["div",{"id":"4","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.4","order":"02.19.004.33129"},["b","4"],"Thy words have upholden him that was falling, and thou hast strengthened the feeble knees."],["div",{"id":"5","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.5","order":"02.19.004.33130"},["b","5"],"But now it is come upon thee, and thou faintest; it toucheth thee, and thou art troubled."],["div",{"id":"6","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.6","order":"02.19.004.33131"},["b","6"],["i","Is"],"not",["i","this"],"thy fear, thy",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_6a"},"confidence"],", thy hope, and the",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_6b"},"uprightness"],"of thy ways?"],["div",{"id":"7","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.7","order":"02.19.004.33132"},["b","7"],"Remember, I pray thee, who",["i","ever"],"perished, being",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_7a"},"innocent"],"? or where were the righteous cut off?"],["div",{"id":"8","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.8","order":"02.19.004.33133"},["b","8"],"Even as I have seen, they that plow iniquity, and",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_8a"},"sow"],"wickedness, reap the same."],["div",{"id":"9","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.9","order":"02.19.004.33134"},["b","9"],"By the blast of God they perish, and by the breath of his nostrils are they consumed."],["div",{"id":"10","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.10","order":"02.19.004.33135"},["b","10"],"The roaring of the lion, and the voice of the fierce lion, and the",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_10a"},"teeth"],"of the young lions, are broken."],["div",{"id":"11","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.11","order":"02.19.004.33136"},["b","11"],"The old lion perisheth for lack of prey, and the stout lion’s whelps are scattered abroad."],["div",{"id":"12","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.12","order":"02.19.004.33137"},["b","12"],"Now a thing was secretly brought to me, and mine ear received a little thereof."],["div",{"id":"13","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.13","order":"02.19.004.33138"},["b","13"],"In thoughts from the visions of the night, when deep sleep falleth on men,"],["div",{"id":"14","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.14","order":"02.19.004.33139"},["b","14"],"Fear came upon me, and trembling, which made all my bones to shake."],["div",{"id":"15","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.15","order":"02.19.004.33140"},["b","15"],"Then a spirit passed before my face; the hair of my flesh stood up:"],["div",{"id":"16","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.16","order":"02.19.004.33141"},["b","16"],"It stood still, but I could not discern the form thereof: an image",["i","was"],"before mine eyes,",["i","there was"],["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_16a"},"silence"],", and I heard a",["sup","b"],["a",{"href":"fn_16b"},"voice"],",",["i","saying,"]],["div",{"id":"17","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.17","order":"02.19.004.33142"},["b","17"],"Shall mortal man be more",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_17a"},"just"],"than God? shall a man be more pure than his maker?"],["div",{"id":"18","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.18","order":"02.19.004.33143"},["b","18"],"Behold, he put no trust in his servants; and his angels he charged with folly:"],["div",{"id":"19","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.19","order":"02.19.004.33144"},["b","19"],"How much less",["i","in"],"them that dwell in houses of",["sup","a"],["a",{"href":"fn_19a"},"clay"],", whose foundation",["i","is"],"in the dust,",["i","which"],"are crushed before the moth?"],["div",{"id":"20","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.20","order":"02.19.004.33145"},["b","20"],"They are destroyed from morning to evening: they perish for ever without any regarding",["i","it."]],["div",{"id":"21","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.21","order":"02.19.004.33146"},["b","21"],"Doth not their excellency",["i","which is"],"in them go away? they die, even without wisdom."]]],"refs":[["div",{"id":"1a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.1a","order":"02.19.004.33147"},["b","1a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/2.11"},"Job 2:11"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/121.10.7-11"},"D&C 121:10 (7–11)"],"."],["div",{"id":"6a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.6a","order":"02.19.004.33149"},["b","6a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/prov/3.26"},"Prov. 3:26"],"."],["div",{"id":"6b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.6b","order":"02.19.004.33151"},["b","6b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/job/1.1"},"Job 1:1"],"."],["div",{"id":"7a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.7a","order":"02.19.004.33153"},["b","7a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/nt/1-cor/10.13"},"1 Cor. 10:13"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/1-ne/22.19"},"1 Ne. 22:19"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/alma/14.11"},"Alma 14:11"],"."],["div",{"id":"8a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.8a","order":"02.19.004.33155"},["b","8a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/harvest"},"TG Harvest"],"."],["div",{"id":"10a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.10a","order":"02.19.004.33157"},["b","10a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/ps/58.6"},"Ps. 58:6"],"."],["div",{"id":"16a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.16a","order":"02.19.004.33159"},["b","16a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/bofm/hel/5.30.30-31"},"Hel. 5:30 (30–31)"],";",["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/dc-testament/dc/85.6.6-7"},"D&C 85:6 (6–7)"],"."],["div",{"id":"16b","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.16b","order":"02.19.004.33161"},["b","16b"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/ot/1-kgs/19.12.11-13"},"1 Kgs. 19:12 (11–13)"],"."],["div",{"id":"17a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.17a","order":"02.19.004.33163"},["b","17a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/justice"},"TG Justice"],"."],["div",{"id":"19a","uri":"/scriptures/ot/job/4.19a","order":"02.19.004.33165"},["b","19a"],["a.scriptureRef",{"href":"/scriptures/tg/man-physical-creation-of"},"TG Man, Physical Creation of"],"."]]}
